6. Simulation Termination Conditions
Q6: When does a simulation end?
- Agent death (natural causes, median age ~80)
- Age cap (e.g., simulate max 100 years, even if agent lives longer)
- Catastrophic bankruptcy (net worth < -$500K and no recovery path)
- Incarceration with life sentence
- Emigration (leave country, outside model scope)
My assumption: End at death or age 100, but track "quality of outcome" - successful retirement vs destitution vs incarcerated vs deceased.
